\id 1TH Meriam Mer - draft material - not consultant checked 
\toc2 1 TESALONIKA 
\toc1 1 TESALONIKA 
\mt1 1 TESALONIKA  
\ip draft by Fr Nagai Tabo, Peter Wickham MER Oct-Nov 87 & Gamalai Passi  
\c 1  
\d MIZMIZ NOSIK 1-10  
\p
\v 1 Iabialam Paulo, Sailas a Timoto, wabim zogometa Tesalonikage muige Baba Ad a Ople Iesu Keriso. Adira omar a mapodan wabim.  
\v 2 Ki gair kerkerge Adi eswao wabim waikelare waba nei odarabgelare kerbi erkepasamge.  
\v 3 Kiki mena wabi wadikepwalare meriba Ad a Baba opem waba dorge owaturge, waba meregsusapit omarge a wa barkak erkepwaikoslare abim meriba Ople Iesu Keriso.  
\v 4 Buai, Adide wabi omarge dikereda, ki umele dale E wabi ditutirda,  
\v 5 Ableglam ki debe mir wabim taisa nole no mir tebteb epe sasrim ko ableglam able mir barkak ike. Wa umele ki nako waurder nade ki wabi doge wadale wabi debeleem.  
\v 6 Wa kerbi doge a Oplege takmeirda. Wa asiasi tidigida a wage mir erpeidarda a sererge baprekerda Lamar Zogolam.  
\v 7 Able gair legize mir irmireda Masedoniage a Akaiage mokakalam pe wawa ikereda.  
\v 8 Oplera mir wabialam ebrerdi nole Masedoniage a Akaiage tebteb epe waba owatur Adi doge able mir ko ebrerdi gair gedge. Nole pa kerbim dike ki waderle daratagrare wabi owaturlam,  
\v 9 Ableglam wader legize kerbi detagreda wa nako wa kerbi derepda a wa nako wa Adim batarda able bes adilam ko agekar a idid Ad irmireda  
\v 10 a iako able werem dikailare mena e kotorlam watabakamu: abra werem Iesu ge e abi eudlam ikiamda a e merbi degderapda adud bodomalam pe tikaseredi.   
\c 2  
\d MIZMIZ 2 NOSIK 7-13  
\p
\v 7 Kiki Kerisora kaimegiz, ki umele kiki ge ki wabi dikerda beberbeber berda, ege ki no sikak urder nade ki wabi doge dale mokakalam apude tabara omaskir onaseseredlare.  
\v 8 Ableglam keriba omar wabim kige no able lu ikerida wabi doge nole debe mir tebteb ki ko geki urder wabi doge sererserer.  
\v 9 Buai, wa dikepwareda keriba au dorge ki a gerger wa nole gewa bodomalam ikelare kiki wabi doge urder geki Agudira debe mir detautlare.  
\v 10 Wa wabu dasmerda a pako Agude dasmeli kiki dale zogozogo, barkak a nole sek amrirkak wabim able leem peiwawa irmireda.  
\v 11 Wa umele uridli ki wabim geki ikelare mokakalam babet waikerer taba omaskirem.  
\v 12 Ki wabi okadeskeda a ki wabi degderapeda a ki wabi sirdaiswereda wa able tonar ge uridwa pe Agudi doge debele ike pe E wabi dabgereda Abi baselaiem a Abi zoromem.  
\v 13 Ki Agudi mena eswao ikereda ableglam Agudira mir bakamuda wabim kerbialam wage erpeidara ableglam Agudira mir ike a nole lera mir ike. Agudira mir pe wabi doge dali pe wawa irmireda.   
\c 4  
\d MIZMIZ 4 NOSIK 13-18  
\p
\v 13 Buai, ki laglag wa umele urder able agekar mir netiba ut erdedi eudge, ia waiakai wa umerkak okasosok urder mokakalam able le nole umerkak nalu pe dikase.  
\v 14 Mi umele uridli merbi nerkeplam Iesu eumida a ko ekiamda, pako mi umele uridli merbi nerkeplam Agudide ia watais Iesui kemem able le ge baumi.  
\v 15 Abialam Oplera mir ki wabi detagreda able le pe kiki mena idid uridli able le ge kerbi dikaireta paki uridli mena Ople watakomer, iaki umerkak nabakiaware kikem able lege ge baumi,  
\v 16 Ableglam Ople ia tababu otabu kotorlam abra mir ia aukelakela waike, a pako kirim angelara kodomir a Agudira burar, able eudle pe Kerisoi doge erdedi ia kikem obakiam.  
\v 17 Keubu mimi pemi mena idid uridli ia mi tatkimdare okakise muige basge a Ople op tadapidare mige.  
\v 18 Wa waba okabaskawem able miru.   